            'Romani 1:2; 4:3; 9:17': '<h3> <span>Romani 1:2</span></h3><p> <span><sup>2&#xA0;</sup>pe care o<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-27933A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-27933A"></sup> f&#x103;g&#x103;duise mai &#xEE;nainte prin<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-27933B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-27933B"></sup> prorocii S&#x103;i &#xEE;n Sfintele Scripturi.</span> </p><h3> <span>Romani 4:3</span></h3><p> <span><sup>3&#xA0;</sup>C&#x103;ci ce zice Scriptura? &#x201E;Avraam<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28026A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28026A"></sup> a crezut pe Dumnezeu, &#x15F;i aceasta i s-a socotit ca neprih&#x103;nire.&#x201D;</span> </p><h3> <span>Romani 9:17</span></h3><p> <span><sup>17&#xA0;</sup>Fiindc&#x103; Scriptura<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28173A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28173A"></sup> zice lui Faraon: &#x201E;Te-am ridicat &#xEE;nadins<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28173B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28173B"></sup>, ca s&#x103;-Mi ar&#x103;t &#xEE;n tine puterea Mea &#x15F;i pentru ca Numele Meu s&#x103; fie vestit &#xEE;n tot p&#x103;m&#xE2;ntul&#x201D;.</span> </p>'
            'Galateni 2:1-10': '<h3> <span>Galateni 2:1-10</span></h3><p><span><span>2&#xA0;</span>Dup&#x103; paisprezece ani, m-am<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29083A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29083A"></sup> suit din nou la Ierusalim &#xEE;mpreun&#x103; cu Barnaba &#x15F;i am luat cu mine &#x15F;i pe Tit.</span> <span><sup>2&#xA0;</sup>M-am suit, &#xEE;n urma unei descoperiri, &#x15F;i le-am<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29084B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29084B"></sup> ar&#x103;tat Evanghelia pe care o propov&#x103;duiesc eu &#xEE;ntre neamuri, &#xEE;ndeosebi celor mai cu vaz&#x103;, ca nu cumva s&#x103; alerg<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29084C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29084C"></sup> sau s&#x103; fi alergat &#xEE;n zadar.</span> <span><sup>3&#xA0;</sup>Nici chiar Tit, care era cu mine, m&#x103;car c&#x103; era grec, n-a fost silit s&#x103; se taie &#xEE;mprejur,</span> <span><sup>4&#xA0;</sup>din pricina fra&#x163;ilor<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29086D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29086D"></sup> mincino&#x15F;i, furi&#x15F;a&#x163;i &#x15F;i strecura&#x163;i printre noi ca s&#x103; p&#xE2;ndeasc&#x103; slobozenia<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29086E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29086E"></sup> pe care o avem &#xEE;n Hristos Isus, cu g&#xE2;nd s&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29086F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29086F"></sup> ne aduc&#x103; la robie;</span> <span><sup>5&#xA0;</sup>noi nu ne-am supus &#x15F;i nu ne-am potrivit lor nicio clip&#x103; m&#x103;car, pentru ca adev&#x103;rul<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29087G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29087G"></sup> Evangheliei s&#x103; r&#x103;m&#xE2;n&#x103; cu voi.</span> <span><sup>6&#xA0;</sup>Cei<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29088H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29088H"></sup> ce sunt socoti&#x163;i ca fiind ceva &#x2013; orice ar fi fost ei, nu-mi pas&#x103;: Dumnezeu<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29088I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29088I"></sup> nu caut&#x103; la fa&#x163;a oamenilor &#x2013; ace&#x15F;tia, zic, ei, cei cu vaz&#x103;, nu<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29088J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29088J"></sup> mi-au ad&#x103;ugat nimic.</span> <span><sup>7&#xA0;</sup>Ba dimpotriv&#x103;, c&#xE2;nd au v&#x103;zut<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29089K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29089K"></sup> c&#x103; mie &#xEE;mi<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29089L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29089L"></sup> fusese &#xEE;ncredin&#x163;at&#x103; Evanghelia pentru cei net&#x103;ia&#x163;i &#xEE;mprejur, dup&#x103; cum lui Petru &#xEE;i fusese &#xEE;ncredin&#x163;at&#x103; Evanghelia pentru cei t&#x103;ia&#x163;i &#xEE;mprejur &#x2013;</span> <span><sup>8&#xA0;</sup>c&#x103;ci Cel ce f&#x103;cuse din Petru apostolul celor t&#x103;ia&#x163;i &#xEE;mprejur f&#x103;cuse<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29090M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29090M"></sup> &#x15F;i din mine apostolul neamurilor<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29090N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29090N"></sup> &#x2013;</span> <span><sup>9&#xA0;</sup>&#x15F;i c&#xE2;nd au cunoscut harul<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29091O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29091O"></sup> care-mi fusese dat, Iacov, Chifa &#x15F;i Ioan, care sunt privi&#x163;i ca st&#xE2;lpi<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29091P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29091P"></sup>, mi-au dat mie &#x15F;i lui Barnaba m&#xE2;na dreapt&#x103; de &#xEE;nso&#x163;ire, ca s&#x103; mergem s&#x103; propov&#x103;duim: noi la neamuri, iar ei la cei t&#x103;ia&#x163;i &#xEE;mprejur.</span> <span><sup>10&#xA0;</sup>Ne-au spus numai s&#x103; ne aducem aminte de cei s&#x103;raci, &#x15F;i chiar a&#x15F;a<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29092Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29092Q"></sup> am &#x15F;i c&#x103;utat s&#x103; fac.</span></p>'
            'Galateni 3:6-14': '<h3> <span>Galateni 3:6-14</span></h3><p> <span><sup>6&#xA0;</sup>Tot a&#x15F;a &#x15F;i &#x201E;Avraam<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29109A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29109A"></sup> a crezut pe Dumnezeu, &#x15F;i credin&#x163;a aceasta i-a fost socotit&#x103; ca neprih&#x103;nire&#x201D;.</span> <span><sup>7&#xA0;</sup>&#xCE;n&#x163;elege&#x163;i &#x15F;i voi, dar, c&#x103; fii ai lui Avraam sunt cei<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29110B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29110B"></sup> ce au credin&#x163;&#x103;.</span> <span><sup>8&#xA0;</sup>Scriptura, de asemenea, fiindc&#x103; prevedea<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29111C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29111C"></sup> c&#x103; Dumnezeu va socoti neprih&#x103;nite pe neamuri prin credin&#x163;&#x103;, a vestit mai dinainte lui Avraam aceast&#x103; veste bun&#x103;: &#x201E;Toate neamurile vor fi binecuv&#xE2;ntate &#xEE;n<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29111D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29111D"></sup> tine&#x201D;.</span> <span><sup>9&#xA0;</sup>A&#x15F;a c&#x103; cei ce se bizuie pe credin&#x163;&#x103; sunt binecuv&#xE2;nta&#x163;i &#xEE;mpreun&#x103; cu Avraam cel credincios.</span> <span><sup>10&#xA0;</sup>C&#x103;ci to&#x163;i cei ce se bizuie pe faptele Legii sunt sub blestem, pentru c&#x103; este scris: &#x201E;Blestemat<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29113E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29113E"></sup> este oricine nu st&#x103;ruie &#xEE;n toate lucrurile scrise &#xEE;n cartea Legii ca s&#x103; le fac&#x103;&#x201D;.</span> <span><sup>11&#xA0;</sup>&#x15E;i c&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29114F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29114F"></sup> nimeni nu este socotit neprih&#x103;nit &#xEE;naintea lui Dumnezeu prin Lege este &#xEE;nvederat, c&#x103;ci &#x201E;cel<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29114G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29114G"></sup> neprih&#x103;nit prin credin&#x163;&#x103; va tr&#x103;i&#x201D;.</span> <span><sup>12&#xA0;</sup>&#xCE;ns&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29115H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29115H"></sup> Legea nu se &#xEE;ntemeiaz&#x103; pe credin&#x163;&#x103;, ci ea zice: &#x201E;Cine<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29115I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29115I"></sup> va face aceste lucruri va tr&#x103;i prin ele&#x201D;.</span> <span><sup>13&#xA0;</sup>Hristos<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29116J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29116J"></sup> ne-a r&#x103;scump&#x103;rat din blestemul Legii, f&#x103;c&#xE2;ndu-Se blestem pentru noi, fiindc&#x103; este scris: &#x201E;Blestemat<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29116K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29116K"></sup> e oricine este at&#xE2;rnat pe lemn&#x201D;,</span> <span><sup>14&#xA0;</sup>pentru ca<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29117L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29117L"></sup> binecuv&#xE2;ntarea vestit&#x103; lui Avraam s&#x103; vin&#x103; peste neamuri &#xEE;n Hristos Isus, a&#x15F;a ca, prin credin&#x163;&#x103;, noi s&#x103; primim Duhul<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29117M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29117M"></sup> f&#x103;g&#x103;duit.</span></p>'
            'Galateni 3:6-8': '<h3> <span>Galateni 3:6-8</span></h3><p> <span><sup>6&#xA0;</sup>Tot a&#x15F;a &#x15F;i &#x201E;Avraam<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29109A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29109A"></sup> a crezut pe Dumnezeu, &#x15F;i credin&#x163;a aceasta i-a fost socotit&#x103; ca neprih&#x103;nire&#x201D;.</span> <span><sup>7&#xA0;</sup>&#xCE;n&#x163;elege&#x163;i &#x15F;i voi, dar, c&#x103; fii ai lui Avraam sunt cei<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29110B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29110B"></sup> ce au credin&#x163;&#x103;.</span> <span><sup>8&#xA0;</sup>Scriptura, de asemenea, fiindc&#x103; prevedea<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29111C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29111C"></sup> c&#x103; Dumnezeu va socoti neprih&#x103;nite pe neamuri prin credin&#x163;&#x103;, a vestit mai dinainte lui Avraam aceast&#x103; veste bun&#x103;: &#x201E;Toate neamurile vor fi binecuv&#xE2;ntate &#xEE;n<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29111D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29111D"></sup> tine&#x201D;.</span> </p>'
            '2 Timotei 3:16': '<h3> <span>2 Timotei 3:16</span></h3><p> <span><sup>16&#xA0;</sup>Toat&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29870A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29870A"></sup> Scriptura este insuflat&#x103; de Dumnezeu &#x15F;i de folos<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29870B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29870B"></sup> ca s&#x103; &#xEE;nve&#x163;e, s&#x103; mustre, s&#x103; &#xEE;ndrepte, s&#x103; dea &#xEE;n&#x163;elepciune &#xEE;n neprih&#x103;nire,</span> </p>'
            'Galateni 3:1-5': '<h3> <span>Galateni 3:1-5</span></h3><p><span><span>3&#xA0;</span>O, galateni nechibzui&#x163;i! Cine<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29104A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29104A"></sup> v-a fermecat<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29104B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29104B"></sup> pe voi &#xEE;naintea ochilor c&#x103;rora a fost zugr&#x103;vit Isus Hristos ca r&#x103;stignit?</span> <span><sup>2&#xA0;</sup>Iat&#x103; numai ce voiesc s&#x103; &#x15F;tiu de la voi: prin faptele Legii a&#x163;i primit voi Duhul<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29105C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29105C"></sup> ori<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29105D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29105D"></sup> prin auzirea credin&#x163;ei?</span> <span><sup>3&#xA0;</sup>Sunte&#x163;i a&#x15F;a de nechibzui&#x163;i? Dup&#x103; ce a&#x163;i &#xEE;nceput<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29106E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29106E"></sup> prin Duhul, vre&#x163;i acum s&#x103; sf&#xE2;r&#x15F;i&#x163;i prin firea p&#x103;m&#xE2;nteasc&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29106F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29106F"></sup>?</span> <span><sup>4&#xA0;</sup>&#xCE;n zadar<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29107G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29107G"></sup> a&#x163;i suferit voi at&#xE2;t de mult? Dac&#x103;, &#xEE;n adev&#x103;r, e &#xEE;n zadar!</span> <span><sup>5&#xA0;</sup>Cel ce<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29108H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29108H"></sup> v&#x103; d&#x103; Duhul &#x15F;i face minuni printre voi le face oare prin faptele Legii sau prin auzirea credin&#x163;ei?</span> </p>'
            'Galateni 3:8,9': '<h3> <span>Galateni 3:8</span></h3><p> <span><sup>8&#xA0;</sup>Scriptura, de asemenea, fiindc&#x103; prevedea<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29111A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29111A"></sup> c&#x103; Dumnezeu va socoti neprih&#x103;nite pe neamuri prin credin&#x163;&#x103;, a vestit mai dinainte lui Avraam aceast&#x103; veste bun&#x103;: &#x201E;Toate neamurile vor fi binecuv&#xE2;ntate &#xEE;n<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29111B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29111B"></sup> tine&#x201D;.</span> </p><h3> <span>Galateni 3:9</span></h3><p> <span><sup>9&#xA0;</sup>A&#x15F;a c&#x103; cei ce se bizuie pe credin&#x163;&#x103; sunt binecuv&#xE2;nta&#x163;i &#xEE;mpreun&#x103; cu Avraam cel credincios.</span> </p>'
            'Romani 13:8-10': '<h3> <span>Romani 13:8-10</span></h3><p><span><sup>8&#xA0;</sup>S&#x103; nu datora&#x163;i nim&#x103;nui nimic, dec&#xE2;t s&#x103; v&#x103; iubi&#x163;i unii pe al&#x163;ii, c&#x103;ci cine<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28275A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28275A"></sup> iube&#x15F;te pe al&#x163;ii a &#xEE;mplinit Legea.</span> <span><sup>9&#xA0;</sup>De fapt: &#x201E;S&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28276B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28276B"></sup> nu preacurve&#x15F;ti, s&#x103; nu furi, s&#x103; nu faci nicio m&#x103;rturisire mincinoas&#x103;, s&#x103; nu pofte&#x15F;ti&#x201D; &#x15F;i orice alt&#x103; porunc&#x103; mai poate fi se cuprind &#xEE;n porunca aceasta: &#x201E;S&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28276C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28276C"></sup> iube&#x15F;ti pe aproapele t&#x103;u ca pe tine &#xEE;nsu&#x163;i&#x201D;.</span> <span><sup>10&#xA0;</sup>Dragostea nu face r&#x103;u aproapelui: dragostea<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28277D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28277D"></sup> deci este &#xEE;mplinirea Legii.</span></p>'
            'Romani 1:2-4': '<h3> <span>Romani 1:2-4</span></h3><p> <span><sup>2&#xA0;</sup>pe care o<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-27933A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-27933A"></sup> f&#x103;g&#x103;duise mai &#xEE;nainte prin<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-27933B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-27933B"></sup> prorocii S&#x103;i &#xEE;n Sfintele Scripturi.</span> <span><sup>3&#xA0;</sup>Ea prive&#x15F;te pe Fiul S&#x103;u, n&#x103;scut<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-27934C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-27934C"></sup> din s&#x103;m&#xE2;n&#x163;a lui David &#xEE;n ce prive&#x15F;te trupul,</span> <span><sup>4&#xA0;</sup>iar &#xEE;n ce prive&#x15F;te<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-27935D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-27935D"></sup> duhul<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-27935E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-27935E"></sup> sfin&#x163;eniei dovedit cu putere<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-27935F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-27935F"></sup> c&#x103; este Fiul lui Dumnezeu, prin &#xEE;nvierea mor&#x163;ilor, adic&#x103; pe Isus Hristos, Domnul nostru,</span> </p>'
